## Pagesmith Site Toolkit

This project uses `@pagesmith/site` on top of `@pagesmith/core`.

- Read `node_modules/@pagesmith/site/ai-guidelines/site-guidelines.md` before changing site wiring.
- Read `node_modules/@pagesmith/site/ai-guidelines/usage.md` for the package workflow.
- Read `node_modules/@pagesmith/site/REFERENCE.md` for CLI, preset, JSX, CSS, runtime, and SSG details.
- Keep content collections and schemas in `@pagesmith/core`.
- Keep site-facing JSX, CSS, runtime JS, and SSG imports in `@pagesmith/site`.
